==Serbian==
===Greeting===
'''Hristos se rodi'''
#[[Merry Christmas]] (''greeting'')
#(''literally''): [[Jesus]] [[was]] [[born]].
*:''Note:  This is only the '''greeting''' part of the greeting.  The reply to the greeting is [[Vaistinu se rodi#Serbian|Vaistinu se rodi]].''
